text:
...Hey, hey, the window's over here.
Look...

Come on, come on... There you go...
Look... There... Oh, by the way...

Sorry to bother you, but
could you wait in the hallway for a bit?

...Not at all.
I won't mind even if you're doing a delightful dance.

Oh, no... There's a butterfly inside the office
right now... Look over there...

I'm trying to let it out outside.
It's fine if you're okay with it, Madoka, but──...
